ご挨拶

日本の民族衣装、友禅染めのきものは、金糸・銀糸の刺繍と共に世界に誇る美であり、古くから伝わる伝統文化です。
その美しさを海外の方々にもお伝えしたいと私ども(株)京都繊維は日本古来の着物をもっと気軽に、
簡単に着て頂けるようにアレンジしました。

スタイルはシンプルになりましたが、伝統の技と心を守る姿勢は創業以来変わらず、図案を描く事から製品の完成まで
社内一貫仕上げをし、厳しい検品の後、国内はもとより広く海外に向け出荷されています。

日本の伝統文化と世界に誇れる美しさを現代のライフスタイルの中に活かし、京友禅・京刺繍を更に世界中に広めていければ、
こんなに嬉しい事はありません。

株式会社　京都繊維
電話: 075-591-3354
FAX: 075-581-8544
所在地: 〒607-8424 京都市山科区御陵原西町42番地


Message from KYOTO SEN'I

We Japanese are very proud of our traditional folk style costume, the kimono. The "Kyo-Yuzen"
dyeing process is a beautiful and quite a famous technique in Japan, as well as the lovely
"Kyo-shishu" Japanese style of embroidery. Our vision is to help everyone personally experience
and feel the beauty of Japanese culture by wearing one of our kimonos.
We create kimonos which are simple, clean cut reduced in style, with beautiful and unique designs.
We conduct every step in manufacturing process ourselves from creating initial designs to
packaging the items directly before shipment, so we are very proud of the very high quality
of our products.
We are working daily to meet the high demand for our products not only domestically in the
Japanese market, but internationally as well.
We passionately are working to create an entirely new value of Japanese style and clothing, 
while building broad awareness of the "Kyo-Yuzen" dyeing process and "Kyo-Shishu" embroidery
style in the context of modern lifestyles across the world.

KYOTO SEN'I CO.,LTD.
